            },
            "type": "acg.display.html",
            "props": {
              "html": "<h2>Source of Truth</h2><div class=\"deps-grid\"><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>View</h3><p><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/perspective/views/index.view.json</code></p><p class=\"deps-note\">Perspective component tree; rebuild with <code>./README.sh perspective</code></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Builder</h3><p><code>guild/web/scripts/perspective-build.js</code></p><p class=\"deps-note\">Reads the view, resolves bindings, emits HTML</p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Output</h3><p><code>index.html</code> (repo root)</p><p class=\"deps-note\">This very page's source-of-truth is the view above — NOT this HTML.</p></div></div>"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "meta": {
              "name": "S2"
            },
            "type": "acg.display.html",
            "props": {
              "html": "<h2>Head Assets (loaded on first paint)</h2><div class=\"deps-grid\"><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Fonts</h3><p><a href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&amp;family=Work+Sans:wght@300;400;600&amp;family=Courier+Prime:wght@400;700\">Google Fonts</a></p><p class=\"deps-note\">Playfair Display · Work Sans · Courier Prime</p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Stylesheet</h3><p><a href=\"guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/style/home.css\"><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/style/home.css</code></a></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Analytics</h3><p><code>G-Z1CEF69ZSH</code></p><p class=\"deps-note\">gtag.js from googletagmanager</p></div></div>"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "meta": {
              "name": "S3"
            },
            "type": "acg.display.html",
            "props": {
              "html": "<h2>Body Scripts (end of body)</h2><div class=\"deps-grid\"><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>home.js</h3><p><a href=\"guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/home.js\"><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/home.js</code></a></p><p class=\"deps-note\">Signatories loader, sign-form handler, smooth-scroll for in-page anchors (SKIPS <code>#/</code> route hashes)</p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>renderer.js</h3><p><a href=\"guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/renderer.js\"><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/renderer.js</code></a></p><p class=\"deps-note\">Client-side view engine: currentRoute, matchRoute, renderNode, loadAllComponents, navigate</p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>ACGRenderer.init</h3><p><code>{siteMap, components, mountPoint, analyticsId}</code></p><p class=\"deps-note\">Inline init call, end of body</p></div></div>"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "meta": {
              "name": "S4"
            },
            "type": "acg.display.html",
            "props": {
              "html": "<h2>Runtime Fetches (on navigation)</h2><div class=\"deps-grid\"><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Site Map</h3><p><a href=\"guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/site-map.json\"><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/site-map.json</code></a></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Registry</h3><p><a href=\"guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/components/registry.json\"><code>components/registry.json</code></a></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Page</h3><p><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/pages/&lt;slug&gt;.page.json</code></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>View</h3><p><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/views/&lt;slug&gt;.view.json</code></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Data</h3><p><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/views/data/&lt;slug&gt;.data.json</code></p></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Components</h3><p><code>guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/components/udts/instances/*.json</code></p><p class=\"deps-note\">All loaded upfront at init, cached for all routes</p></div></div>"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "meta": {
              "name": "S5"
            },
            "type": "acg.display.html",
            "props": {
              "html": "<h2>Perspective Components Used by Shell</h2><div class=\"deps-grid\"><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Layout</h3><ul><li><code>acg.container.dock-layout</code></li><li><code>acg.dock.north</code></li><li><code>acg.container.body</code></li><li><code>acg.dock.south</code></li></ul></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Navigation</h3><ul><li><code>acg.nav.top</code></li><li><code>acg.display.link</code></li><li><code>acg.nav.cta</code></li></ul></div><div class=\"deps-card\"><h3>Content</h3><ul><li><code>acg.display.emblem</code></li><li><code>acg.display.heading</code></li><li><code>acg.display.text</code></li><li><code>acg.display.html</code></li><li><code>acg.card.manifesto</code></li></ul></div></div><p class=\"deps-note\">Full catalog: <a href=\"guild/Enterprise/L2/hmi/web/perspective/components/registry.json\">registry.json</a></p>"
            },
            "children": []
